markdownRemark.html: A new reading of Aldo's humanism, emphasizing his early career as a grammar master and its effect on his later work as a printer, is Brian Richardson, "'Optimo humanista e greco': Aldus Manutius' Career in Venice in the Eyes of Marin Sanudo," Erasmus Studies 35 (2015), 181-209.
